data.description:
Welcome to this stately brick traditional home. We are featuring First-floor primary bedroom with an ensuite and a great location. The columns and front porch welcome you to the house, and upon entering, the beautiful foyer with formal and living room, open kitchen with granite countertops and all appliances conveying.  The first-floor primary suite is just beside the laundry for convenience, and there are four additional bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms upstairs.  The basement is finished and ready for entertainment! With a half bath and garage access.

Our preferred lender with Summit Funding is offering .5% up to 5k to both the seller and the buyer if you use them.
